message: Hello, thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
I can't believe the terrible service I've received from your company!
I'm deeply sorry to hear about your experience. I'm here to help. Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Thank you for confirming. Could you also provide me with your date of birth?
Great, lastly, can you confirm your first line of address and postcode?
Thank you for completing security. I understand you're unhappy with our service. How can we find a way forward to resolve this issue?
I've had the worst experience with your claims process. It's been a nightmare!
I apologize for any inconvenience this has caused you. Let's see if we can work towards a resolution. A possible solution could be to escalate your claim for a faster review. Would that work for you?
I need this sorted as soon as possible. I can't believe the lack of care shown to me during this difficult time.
I completely understand the urgency, and I'm here to help. How about we expedite the review process for your claim? Does this work for you?
I guess that would be better than nothing. Please make sure it's done quickly.
I'll ensure we prioritize your claim for a swift review. Thank you for your feedback. Is there anything else I can assist you with?
No, that's all for now. But I still can't believe the poor service I've received.
I understand your frustration, and I truly appreciate your patience during this time. Thank you for reaching out. Have a great day.
